{"tid":2204784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局昨更新中小學文化及歷史科教材 包括TVB及團結香港基金製作的短片 並編制工作紙供學生使用","createTime":"2020-09-16T10:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T10:09:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94516e0cf70aa82ae3671695477544b8b3a38ccb","tid":2204784,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"教育局昨日向中小學分發及更新學與教材料，主要涉及中國文化及歷史，例如「中華經典名句」、「詩情畫意」古詩學與教資源等等。其中，教育局向中、小學校長建議採用 TVB 製作的《歷史有話說》系列短片，配合學習香港歷史、近代中國國情。短片由團結香港基金冠名贊助，教育局亦向學校提供團結香港基金轄下「中國文化研究院」配合短片編制的工作紙，供中小學使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%B4%8A%E5%8A%A9-tvb-%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E7%8D%B2%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%88%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90-%E8%87%AA%E5%AD%B8%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B%E5%8D%83%E5%AD%97%E8%AC%9B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95/?fbclid=IwAR1pQivhS4efalPVOCfM2eljxjz54onvVdZHQ14vjVA1jbuOju2zJsEwW38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25B4%258A%25E5%258A%25A9-tvb-%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2588%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259D%2590-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%25AD%2597%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1pQivhS4efalPVOCfM2eljxjz54onvVdZHQ14vjVA1jbuOju2zJsEwW38&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=b8815ac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2